(42, 8, 43, 14, 16, 12, 12, 'spent all her living upon physicians', 'Seeking Healing from Physicians', 'Both passages emphasize the futility of seeking healing solely from physicians. The woman in Luke and Asa in Chronicles both faced severe health issues and sought medical help without finding relief.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
